{"tid":1417462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請咁多位在任何情況下都唔好同勇武手足割席..","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:27.000Z","uid":5890,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee9f48857bc75ebaed76cf54e600bc50028af3a","tid":1417462,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"請咁多位在任何情況下都唔好同勇武手足割席..<br />\n只要佢地做既野係對住..黑警..政府..黑社會..都唔好割席..<br />\n點解黑警可以去得咁盡...<br />\n因為佢地背後既人知道黑警做既野係錯晒都好..但都需要呢一股力量去幫佢完成...<br />\n而黑警之所以可以去得咁盡..就係知道有人係背後支撐住佢地...<br />\n<br />\n掉轉諗下..佢地如果知道佢地隨時比人割席....仲點會扑市民扑得咁落力..<br />\n<br />\n所以勇武手足都一樣..<br />\n如果你因為佢做既野而割席...好快佢地就唔敢再咁勇武...<br />\n然後又會變返大遊行.一樣咁..無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fed5e99528b6efa0dad81c856273cd2bb5d683","tid":1417462,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n召喚戰士一人一信<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對黑警加人工! </span></strong></span>黑警你憑咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n呢兩個月受屈市民可以加返自己個人經歷!!!<br />\n記得改wordings!!!幫手推<br />\n<br />\n弱弱的補一句，大家都可以向紀員會提議黑警減薪的🤫🤫🤫"},{"pid":"fd606f55f3aecfa4143cc63750c397d2ff3bfdd2","tid":1417462,"uid":42404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"和理非自己諗下有咩搞好過"},{"pid":"2d46c6c07539870600896fdde6aee68abe30fbcf","tid":1417462,"uid":5890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"請支持勇武手足<br />\n<br />\n佢地係用自己未來去替你完成你唔敢做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e6d425918daf9b4193219f5ccce8aeb490ed58","tid":1417462,"uid":79451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:43:16.000Z","msg":"冇人要割席"},{"pid":"af0e27f096c43ece5e0815733821eb320e670b25","tid":1417462,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"每次有人話放火掟警署燒警署暴力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得反問佢掟中燒中幾多個警察</span></span>，再講返每次有幾多手足頭破血流<br />\n咁都冇人復仇上心襲擊行街警察，只係破壞警署，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代表我哋係用破壞警署嚟表達對整個軍警政權嘅不滿</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋正正係對準用黑警暴力打壓市民發聲嘅政權，而唔係針對警察發洩怒氣，所以先攻擊警署唔攻擊警察</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14a51c508d813ed82dffefa2f0e22fa34b14b01","tid":1417462,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1e6d425918daf9b4193219f5ccce8aeb490ed58","tid":1417462,"uid":79451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:43:16.000Z","msg":"冇人要割席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"出面好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa3f2fa546de468081e7364238e92b9bbc9ac1e","tid":1417462,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f858542c5e70b7ca3f835b9eaf86830c3701a35a","tid":1417462,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"we stand together!"},{"pid":"11e7e6e9c758cfaeaf6b8a8cab8780a8dbf74f00","tid":1417462,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74a3c2273622192ce00065b9f26fbb45f37ac24d","tid":1417462,"uid":180168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"割閪咩<br />\n係叫前線冷靜, 諗一下<br />\n唔好下下上腦<br />\n<br />\n今日無啦啦行動, 罷工嘅NOISE 就畀你地蓋過晒<br />\n都唔知罷黎做乜"},{"pid":"915f407082e72023b6e0312bffc3d0eeea7